465
00:34:53,929 --> 00:34:57,029
Il a un sacré culot, ce gamin.

466
00:34:59,029 --> 00:35:03,339
Mais il sait flairer l'argent,

467
00:35:04,239 --> 00:35:05,339
comme toi.

468
00:35:05,839 --> 00:35:07,269
